  "description": "A vibrant hummingbird perches delicately on a thin, bare branch against a backdrop of blurred, lush green foliage. The hummingbird's head displays iridescent red and emerald green plumage. Its body is a muted green-gray, transitioning to a darker, almost black tail with a hint of purple iridescence. The branch curves gently, and the background is an out-of-focus wash of varying shades of green, hinting at a dense forest or garden. There are also some bright, out-of-focus white spots that resemble sunlight filtering through leaves. The bird appears alert and is positioned facing slightly upwards.",
